    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve well as a dependable commuter for a buyer comfortable with some cosmetic and minor mechanical upkeep. The body has several visible scuffs and a few small dings consistent with its age, and the interior shows noticeable wear on the upholstery and floor mats. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, though it may soon require routine maintenance such as new brake pads and a tire rotation. While it isn't in showroom condition, it offers solid transportation for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a reasonable price.",
