    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits a concours-level exterior finish paired with an interior that remains in showroom-original state. Mechanically flawless and rigorously inspected, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking an uncompromising driving experience. Every detail reflects a pedigree of meticulous care and absolute integrity.",
      "price": 47900.0,
